title: Doomed Minion Icon
body: I still have not received the Doomed Minion Icon for completing the minigame back during the Teemoing. I know it takes awhile to send out the icons, so hopefully this post isn't too soon.

replies.body:
As far as I'm aware, the icons should be distributed by now. Your best bet is to contact Riot Games Player Support to see what's going on. For more information on contacting Player Support, check out this guide:

http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support-oce/8YAWjuqf-your-unofficial-guide-to-creating-player-support-requests

Cheers!
